  <div class="panel">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>tracking</h1>
      <h2 class="h-sm">know where your glasses are outdoors</h2>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="eight columns">
          <p>Throughout the day as you wear your glasses and carry your phone, the Tzukuri app updates a map to show you the current location of your glasses by recording your phone's GPS position. The app only tracks your glasses when they're nearby, e.g when you're wearing or carrying them.</p>
          <p>We know when they're nearby because they'll connect to your phone automatically - Tzukuri glasses contain the world's smallest Bluetooth Low Energy device which communicates with the Tzukuri app and can connect over approximately 15m.</p>
          <p>When your glasses disconnect the app stops tracking their location, and you can see their last known location on the map.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="four columns">
          <%= image_tag 'screenshots/tracking.png' %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

