          <%= image_tag 'glasses/ive-profile-charger.jpg' %>
        </div>
        <div class="seven columns">
          <p>The silver zinc battery used in Tzukuri glasses is chemically free from the overheating and explosion issues that affect Lithium Ion batteries (used by most consumer electronic devices). With the battery kept so close to your head, and for long periods of time, it was important to select a battery that wouldn't risk your safety.</p>
          <p>A fully charged battery can last up to <em>30 days</em> depending on use, and when low can be recharged with the included USB charger. A depleted battery takes around <em>4 hours</em> to charge.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
